attributes.title: Podcast But Outside Da Club (Simply Chaotic)
attributes.caption: Guests include a catcalling no-fapper, a TV actor, and way too many drunk people.
attributes.description: Guests include a catcalling no-fapper with tons of confidence, an actor celebrating his birthday, a woman who is "not a ho", and Ally Hidalgo. Recorded on Spring Street in Downtown Los Angeles.
attributes.display_title: Podcast But Outside Da Club (Simply Chaotic)

attributes.title: We Invited Tinder Dates To Meet Us On The Podcast For The First Time
attributes.caption: First dates live on the podcast!
attributes.description: We each found girls on Tinder to agree to go on "first dates" with us live on our podcast. Do we fall in love? Do they? Do YOU? Watch to find the answers to this and more.
attributes.display_title: We Invited Tinder Dates To Meet Us On The Podcast For The First Time

attributes.title: Blind Date with a Porn Star
attributes.caption: A pornstar DMed Andrew asking to be a guest, so he set her up on a date with Cole! How nice.
attributes.description: A pornstar DMed Andrew asking to be a guest, so he set her up on a date with Cole! How nice. Other guests include a water treatment worker and a group of young hip models. Recorded in front of Grand Central Market in Downtown Los Angeles.
attributes.display_title: Blind Date with a Porn Star

attributes.title: "Black Market" Haul with Chris Fleming
attributes.caption: Guests include a preacher, a very sweet Austrian tourist, and Chris Fleming with some illegal goods.
attributes.description: Guests include a preacher who moved to the midwest to save a failing church, an Austrian tourist inquisitive about life in LA, and the wonderful Chris Fleming as he shares his "black market" haul. Recorded on Colorado Blvd in Pasadena, CA.

attributes.title: Podcast But At A Trump Rally
attributes.caption: Guests include an ecstatic Trump supporter and a woman who leads us in prayer.
attributes.description: We went to a Trump rally to chat with folks about politics. Guests include a wildly high-energy Trump supporter from Chicago whose last name is Trunk, a woman who leads us in prayer for Trump's recovery, and some on-duty police officers staring at us the whole time. Recorded October 3rd, 2020 on Wilshire Blvd in Koreatown, Los Angeles.
attributes.display_title: Podcast But At A Trump Rally

attributes.title: Podcast But Outside Skechers (ft. CaptainSparklez!)
attributes.caption: Guests include a Skechers employee, a weed-loving hairdresser, and CaptainSparklez.
attributes.description: We set up outside the iconic shoe store Skechers (crazy there's no "t" in there, huh?)! Guests include a fearless, weed-smoking hairdresser, a guy who oversees movie contracts, our friend from YouTube, CaptainSparklez, and even a real life Skechers employee who took a break from the sneaker grind to come say hi. Recorded on N San Fernando Blvd in Burbank, Carlyfarnia.

attributes.title: Podcast But Outside Olive Garden
attributes.caption: Guests include a rapper and his beat-maker (who once bought Subway for Kanye), plus a young psychic who sells text message tarot readings on Etsy.
attributes.description: We're back on the restaurant scene, this time in front of world-renowned Italian powerhouse Olive Garden. Guests include a rapper and his beat-maker (who once bought Subway for Kanye), plus a young psychic who sells text message tarot readings on Etsy. Recorded on Brand Blvd in Glendale, California.

attributes.title: Podcast But Outside GAP
attributes.description:
You can all stop asking, we finally filmed in front of Gap! Guests include teens on their way to do nitrous, a man who likes to let loose in the pandemic, and a woman whose friend makes clothes for Kanye! Filmed on San Fernando Blvd in Burbank, California.

attributes.title: Podcast But At A Skatepark
attributes.description:
'Tis the season-- to shred! Guests include a young out-of-work musician looking for love, a mega rad dad who started a non-profit to help poor kids get new skate gear, and the most polite teenager in the world. Featuring an epic fall. Recorded November 15th at the Chevy Chase Skatepark in Los Angeles.
